data.description: Whether you're looking for a place to call home, an investment property, or a combination of both, this property has it all. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to secure your slice of small-town paradise. Nestled in the charming community of Philipsburg, this delightful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is the epitome of comfort and convenience. Boasting a prime location, an inviting interior, and a 1967 BROADMORE 12X60 trailer used as a rental, this property offers the perfect blend of family living and investment opportunity. More Photos coming soon.  Call Charity at 406-529-4764 or your real estate professional to set up a showing. No showings till Monday October 30th.
